# Mutant reseerch in drosophila genomic data

MutantResearch finds specific mutations, and returns the number of matchs and mismatchs in multiple sequencing files

## Preconditions 

1) [git](https://git-scm.com/downloads) 
2) [docker](https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/) with docker compose 

## Installation 

```bash
git clone https://github.com/tu-usuario/tu-proyecto.git
cd tu-proyecto
docker build -t tu-usuario/tu-proyecto .
docker-compose up
```

## Launching

1) Open docker desktop
2) Start research mutantResearch multi-container (if not already running)
3) [Access](https://localhost:8000) 

## Ussage

Specific line = detailed results containing reads and alignement with referential sequence

Multiple lines = Simple results:
    - If the alignement has already being done, existing result will be returned. To evitate this situation select param "savesaveInDb" = false

Max file size = 50 Gb

